data.title: 503 Area Code, Oregon
data.meta_description: 503 area code is a telephone area code in the North American Numbering Plan for Portland and the surrounding area in the northwestern region of Oregon
data.text:
503 area code is a telephone area code in the North American Numbering Plan (NANP) for Portland and the surrounding area in the northwestern region of the state of Oregon, United States. The area code was one of the original area codes created in 1947.

Some of the cities served by the 503 area code include Portland, Salem, Gresham, Hillsboro, Beaverton, Aloha, Tigard, Lake Oswego, Keizer and more.
